{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5a585d0d41","title":"让全世界都能听到我们的声音","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"15d6bc324a","index":0,"year":1955,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"5a585d0d41"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"ad0c608e45","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"5a585d0d41","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东针对当时新华社在发展国外工作方面思想保守、行动退缓的情况所作的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3108ef8e78","type":"title","text":"让全世界都能听到我们的声音！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"5a585d0d41"},{"id":"ad0c608e45","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社这几年做了一些工作。但是，驻外记者派得太少，没有自己的消息，有，也太少。为什么不派？没有干部？中国这么天，抽不出人？是不是中宣部过去没有管？","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"5a585d0d41"},{"id":"5fa86aadbd","type":"paragraph","text":"应该天发展，尽快做到在世界各地都能派有自己的记者，发出自己的消息。把地球管起来，让全世界都能听到我们的声音。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"5a585d0d41"}],"page":{"id":"08dd8cc5cc","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"5a585d0d41","start":122,"end":122}}}},"__N_SSG":true}